channel.title: Sword too great for RuneScape
channel.description:
Here's a sword I am making. Currently has a total of 3009 faces. Hope Dylan likes the title :o. This is a WIP, but I will actually finish this one. If you want it you'll have to buy it from R-S for 10$. I just have one question. What are the rules about selling other peoples concept art? I have seen people sell pokemon on turbosquid and I know pokemon is copywrited. So I was wondering if I could sell this on turbosquid. And with no further ado, my sword! [img]http://img718.imageshack.us/img718/89/swordupdate1.jpg[/img] Wireframe:http://www.moparisthebest.com/Themes/core/images/bbc/bold.gif [img]http://img812.imageshack.us/img812/3091/swordupdate1wireframe.jpg[/img] Document Information: [img]http://img717.imageshack.us/img717/8161/sworddoc.jpg[/img]
[b]Update: 1/26/11[/b] Sword: [img]http://img593.imageshack.us/img593/2650/swordupdate3.jpg[/img] Wireframe (For a full wireframe just compare above wireframe with this one): [img]http://img842.imageshack.us/img842/4840/swordupdate2wireframe.jpg[/img] [img]http://img821.imageshack.us/img821/7016/swordupdate3wireframe.jpg[/img] Document Information: [img]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/4237/swordupdate3docinfo.jpg[/img]
[b]Update: 1/30/11[/b] [img]http://img441.imageshack.us/img441/4505/swordupdate4.jpg[/img] [img]http://img402.imageshack.us/img402/7217/swordupdatesmooth4.jpg[/img] [img]http://img39.imageshack.us/img39/5562/swordupdatehard4.jpg[/img] [img]http://img109.imageshack.us/img109/2659/swordupdated4.jpg[/img]

item.description:

Posted this on FrugooScape and this is what they said haha.

Probably a leeched 3D model, and opened it in Metaseq. It has high polys, not meant for an RSPS, but the polys can be reduced and it can be mimic'd at a low poly form. Bitch please, I model too, but I'm legit. Oh and welcome(1st post)
A credible person posts proof, not just a screenshot of the model. Proof including: Progress reports, proof of non-release, etc. http://www.tineye.com/search/9c2bd08...387df5b2db550/ But that doesn't mean there was a screenshot in the place he downloaded it. Probably downloaded + Screenshotted

I’m simply asking for proof

So then I posted this.

Proof enough?
Here’s a 1957 Thunderbird I’m working on next. I’ve been modeling for almost 1.5 years now. My MoparScape account… and the wireframe. Ask for anything and I’ll supply it.

Edit: Sorry I’m only allowed 4 img tags. Just going to have to use the links.

Sure, but it's also possible to change to wireframe mode, screenshot, delete the end, take screenshots. Unsmooth edges, take screenshots. But I guess I'll believe him this time.
I'm at a loss for how stubborn they are.
